Do what I do: down a lot of sugar and just type until you're about to fall asleep. ...that may not be the best, actually.

Motivation is different for everyone. For me, the sheer happiness of seeing people get some enjoyment from my work is motivation enough. If you want to write, and don't feel it right now, then don't! Let the ideas brew in your head, jot em down, and when you DO feel up to it, write like there's no tomorrow.
